    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "f27f9aef21b87539",
      "text": "Crypto[currency] will be much stronger after this, as banks enter the custodial market. They have charters, audits, BSA officers, training, oversight, transparency to the board, and insurance."
    },
